      "description": "Fix: on networks that require a proxy (common on corporate machines), Cited's query to claude could silently hang and time out instead of failing fast -- Obsidian's process doesn't inherit the login shell's proxy env vars. Now forwards the login shell's environment to the spawned claude process.",
